      <h1>HSA Contribution Limits 2026: Rules and Tax Benefits</h1>
      <p>The projected 2026 HSA contribution limits are $4,400 for self-only HDHP coverage and $8,750 for family coverage &mdash; up from $4,300 and $8,550 in 2025. Account holders 55 and older can contribute an additional $1,000...</p>
