        <h2>Projected 2026 HSA Contribution Limits</h2>

        <div class="kf-grid">
          <div class="kf-item"><div class="kf-label">Self-Only Coverage</div><div class="kf-value green">~$4,400</div><div class="kf-sub">Up from $4,300 in 2025<span style="font-size:.7rem;background:#fef3c7;color:#92400e;border-radius:4px;padding:2px 5px;margin-left:6px;">Projected</span></div></div>
